SUMMARY:Lunch Ladies
DTSTAMP:20260316T010553Z
DTSTART:20260319T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the ladies in our church every 3rd Thursday of the month f
	or lunch and fellowship! Location rotates\, RSVP and check the info center
	 or app for location!  Please RSVP so we know how big of a table to reserv
